ABOUT


This pre-owned, Omega Speedmaster Date 323.21.40.40.02.001 is in like new condition. The watch comes as a full set (undated warranty card), along with 1 year warranty from The Watch Village.




All of our watches undergo a thorough inspection of accuracy, functionality and condition to meet our strict standards. Additionally, we check each watch against records to ensure authenticity and ownership status.




This rare Speedmaster features a striking silver dial that is decorated with gold accents from the hands, numeral markers and complication outlines. A contrasting 18K yellow gold tachymetre bezel sits upon a 40mm stainless steel casebody, which is attached to a matching stainless-steel bracelet. All powered by the Omega Calibre 1164 automatic movement.
